model.name: Stella Wedge Sandal
model.disambiguatingDescription: Crafted from soft lambskin, the Stella wedge sandal is a sleek, elegant design with a distinctive curved heel. The upper features two padded straps for a cushiony effect, which are adjusted with velcro. A delicate LV Circle signature accessorizes the ankle strap, while a padded footbed provides extra comfort.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Black
  • Lambskin
  • Adjustable velcro straps
  • Padded footbed
  • Leather outsole
  • 9.5 cm / 3.7-inch wedge heel
  • LV Circle accessory
  • Made in Italy
